high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk past the green table then turn right and take two steps then turn right to face the green table.
Pick up the tomato that's to the right of the spatula on the table.
Turn left and walk a step forward then turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk back to the green table.
Put the tomato under the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the other side of the green table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink to your left.
Place the tomato inside the sink, wash the tomato and remove it.
Turn around to face the green table.
Place the washed tomato on the green table.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tomato on the green table.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn right. Move toward the fridge and turn right to face the island.
Pick up the tomato from the center of the counter.
Take the tomato and turn around to the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the tomato.
Carry the tomato and turn around to the island.
Place the tomato on the counter, in front of the sale.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a tomato and place it on the counter.
